Hello,

file _atlassian-jira.log_ is a moving target, it will be created in the CWD where the launch script is run and so on.
Since _log4j.properties_ can take variable substitution it would be handy to edit the Appender definition as in:
{noformat}
log4j.appender.filelog.File=${catalina.base}/logs/atlassian-jira.log
{noformat}
to pin the path to a reasonable location

Regards,
Edoardo

