It would be great if JIRA had heatmaps that could be used to indicate the breakdown of components by a user.  At a glance you could see how many bugs Joe Average had worked on in User Management, Workflow or Web Interface, which would help give an idea of how appropriate the user might be to answer a question.  

I imagine this works for any filter, 2 dimensional type data.
